Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Holiday reading
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b040brt8
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 19 Mar 1978
What to read on holiday. The A to Z of surprises in the Manhattan telephone directory. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less